title: Corona maker's profit more than doubles
text:
Corona maker's profit more than doubles 4:10pm BST - 00:51 
Constellation Brands' quarterly profit more than doubled and easily beat analysts' estimates. As Fred Katayama reports, demand for Corona and Modelo beers drove sales sharply higher. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
